{"tid":814402,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"其實玩交友app識人唔係問題 但要有技巧","createTime":"2018-09-11T08:19:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-11T10:04:03.000Z","uid":100809,"like":28,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"5e1615b19c4e73995b4ac646c642be54a3848441","tid":814402,"uid":100809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T08:19:22.000Z","msg":"好多人問交友app係咪好多厹 係咪冇真心 係咪只為食女<br />\n其實唔係 交友app都有好多真心交友既人<br />\n但問題係點解咁多人話識到player厹  因為你識人方法有問題<br />\n<br />\n正常一個女人出post 除非你icon自爆自己係豬西肥西<br />\n而太多人add就係死因<br />\n<br />\n人多你就冇興趣同每個人詳傾 久而久之就用簡單分類法<br />\n由於多人add 咩風趣幽默開場白都見過哂 男人開頭淨係得句hi已經比條女歸類為無聊厹 藍剔收你皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但女人忽略左一樣野 你就話多人撩乜都見過哂姐 但我地好仔果d唔係追女經驗豐富 鬼識風趣開場白<br />\n咪唯有say hi做開場白囉<br />\n<br />\n就係咁港女就揀走左一堆好仔"},{"pid":"d94cb97ccda0260cd61592a5413f9e7a5e7fd746","tid":814402,"uid":198065,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T08:21:27.000Z","msg":"睇相都知對方係邊類型，一睇已經可以篩走七成fuckboys"},{"pid":"c243e1a9aba03d297c91547e3e533d8a91b470b5","tid":814402,"uid":168920,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d94cb97ccda0260cd61592a5413f9e7a5e7fd746","tid":814402,"uid":198065,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T08:21:27.000Z","msg":"睇相都知對方係邊類型，一睇已經可以篩走七成fuckboys"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T08:23:48.000Z","msg":"點先叫fkboy"},{"pid":"cc0e3d6ce142ae7024cf9200e031797d6d74cd34","tid":814402,"uid":198065,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c243e1a9aba03d297c91547e3e533d8a91b470b5","tid":814402,"uid":168920,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d94cb97ccda0260cd61592a5413f9e7a5e7fd746","tid":814402,"uid":198065,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T08:21:27.000Z","msg":"睇相都知對方係邊類型，一睇已經可以篩走七成fuckboys"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T08:23:48.000